library(openxlsx)
## Warning: package 'openxlsx' was built under R version 3.4.4
library(rEDM)
## Warning: package 'rEDM' was built under R version 3.4.4
# Read the xlsx file.
df_rate <- read.xlsx("/Users/ryogamisu/iGEM2018/Dengue-Prediction/denguevirus_infected_in_Bankok.xlsx", sheet = "Rate", rows = 1:28)
df_rate_each <- df_rate[, c("DEN1_rate", "DEN2_rate", "DEN3_rate", "DEN4_rate")]
Year <- df_rate[, "Year"]

df_rate_each_simplex <- apply(df_rate_each, 2, simplex, stats_only = F, lib = c(1, 27), pred = c(1, 27))
## Warning in model$run(): Found overlap between lib and pred. Enabling cross-
## validation with exclusion radius = 0.
## Warning in model$run(): Found overlap between lib and pred. Enabling cross-
## validation with exclusion radius = 0.

## Warning in model$run(): Found overlap between lib and pred. Enabling cross-
## validation with exclusion radius = 0.

## Warning in model$run(): Found overlap between lib and pred. Enabling cross-
## validation with exclusion radius = 0.
{plot(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN1_rate$rho, ylim = c(0, 1), col = "black", ylab = "rho", type = "l", main = "rho about each data", sub = "Black:DEN1_rate, Red:DEN2_rate, Bule:Den3_rate, Green:DEN4_rate")
lines(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN2_rate$rho, col = "red")
lines(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN3_rate$rho, col = "blue")
lines(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN4_rate$rho, col = "green")
}

best_E_rate <- sapply(df_rate_each_simplex, function(df) {
    df$E[which.max(df$rho)] 
})

{plot(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN1_rate$model_output[[best_E_rate["DEN1_rate"]]]$obs, type = "l")
lines(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN1_rate$model_output[[best_E_rate["DEN1_rate"]]]$pred, type = "l", col = "red")
plot(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN2_rate$model_output[[best_E_rate["DEN2_rate"]]]$obs, type = "l")
lines(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN2_rate$model_output[[best_E_rate["DEN2_rate"]]]$pred, type = "l", col = "red")
plot(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN3_rate$model_output[[best_E_rate["DEN3_rate"]]]$obs, type = "l")
lines(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN3_rate$model_output[[best_E_rate["DEN3_rate"]]]$pred, type = "l", col = "red")
plot(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN4_rate$model_output[[best_E_rate["DEN4_rate"]]]$obs, type = "l")
lines(df_rate_each_simplex$DEN4_rate$model_output[[best_E_rate["DEN4_rate"]]]$pred, type = "l", col = "red")}

concatenated_12 <- c(df_rate_each$DEN1_rate, df_rate_each$DEN2_rate)
lib_1 <- c(1, length(df_rate_each$DEN1_rate))
lib_2 <- length(df_rate_each$DEN1_rate) + c(1, length(df_rate_each$DEN2_rate))

simplex_out_1 <- simplex(concatenated_12, lib = lib_1, pred = lib_1, silent = TRUE)
best_E_1 <- simplex_out_1$E[which.max(simplex_out_1$rho)]
copred_1_to_2 <- simplex(concatenated_12, lib = lib_1, pred = lib_2, E = best_E_1)

simplex_out_2 <- simplex(concatenated_12, lib = lib_2, pred = lib_2, silent = TRUE)
best_E_2 <- simplex_out_2$E[which.max(simplex_out_2$rho)]
copred_2_to_1 <- simplex(concatenated_12, lib = lib_2, pred = lib_1, E = best_E_2)

groups <- c("prediction of 1 (from 1)", 
            "coprediction of 1 (from 2)", 
            "prediction of 2 (from 2)", 
            "coprediction of 2 (from 1)")
to_plot <- data.frame(label = factor(groups, levels = groups), 
                      rbind(simplex_out_1[which.max(simplex_out_1$rho), ], 
                            copred_2_to_1, 
                            simplex_out_2[which.max(simplex_out_2$rho), ], 
                            copred_1_to_2)
)

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(to_plot, aes(x = label, y = rho)) + 
    geom_col() + theme_bw() + 
    theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1))
